#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:698
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Files and directories can be transferred to a mounted share by dragging "
#| "them over its icon in the view and drop them there. By default the data "
#| "will be moved to the share. To copy it, hold down the &Ctrl; key while "
#| "you are dragging and dropping it. The transfer will only be successful if "
#| "the share was mounted with read and write permissions."
msgid ""
"To avoid the popup menu, press the &Shift; key for moving, the &Ctrl; key "
