"edukas ainult siis, kui ressurss on ühendatud lugemis- ja kirjutamisõigusega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:699
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can drag a share icon from within the shares view onto the desktop or "
#| "into another application (&eg; &dolphin;) and drop it there. You will "
#| "then maybe get a popup menu asking you if you want to copy, link or move "
