"uus asukoht tekstikasti. Tunnustatakse ka asukohamuutujaid, näiteks $HOME."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3251
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "For each share you synchronize, a new subdirectory below this prefix will "
#| "be generated. If you want to synchronize the contents of a share to a "
#| "different folder, you can define it in the <link linkend="
