msgid ""
"For each share you synchronize, a new subdirectory below this prefix will be "
"generated. If you want to synchronize the contents of a share to a different "
"folder, you can define it in the <link linkend=\"shares_view_synchronization"
"\">synchronization dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Iga sünkroonitava ressursi jaoks luuakse prefiksi alla uus alamkataloog. Kui "
"soovid sünkroonida ressursi sisu mõne muu kataloogiga, tuleb see määrata "
"<link linkend=\"mainwindow_shares_synchronization\">sünkroonimisdialoogis</"
"link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3252
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: <filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/smb4k_sync/</filename>"
msgstr "Vaikimisi: <filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/smb4k_sync/</filename>"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3264
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archive mode"
msgstr "Säilitamisrežiim"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3267
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Option: <option>-a</option>/<option>--archive</option>, same as <option>-"
#| "rlptgoD</option> (no <option>-H</option>)"
msgid ""
"Option: <option>-a</option>/<option>--archive</option>, same as <option>-"
"rlptgoD</option> (no <option>-A</option>, <option>-X</option>, <option>-U</"
"option>, <option>-N</option>, <option>-H</option>)"
msgstr ""
"Valik: <option>-a</option>/<option>--archive</option>, sama mis <option>-"
"rlptgoD</option> (ilma valikuta <option>-H</option>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch the archive mode on. This is a quick way of saying you want recursion "
"and want to preserve almost everything. Note that <option>-a</option> does "
"not preserve hardlinks (<option>-H</option>), access control lists (ACLs, "
"<option>-A</option>), extended attributes (xattrs, <option>-X</option>), "
"access (use) times (<option>-U</option>) nor create times (<option>-N</"
"option>). You must separately specify these options. The only exception to "
"the above equivalence is when <option>--files-from</option> is specified, in "
"which case <option>-r</option> is not implied."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3269
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Note that <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
#| "refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> can only "
#| "detect hard links if both parts of the link are in the list of files "
#| "being sent."
msgid ""
"In case you do not want to run <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> in archive mode, choose the appropriate "
"arguments in the settings yourself."
msgstr ""
"Pane tähele, et <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> suudab püsilinke tuvastada ainult siis, "
"kui üle kantakse lingi mõlemad pooled."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3275
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recurse into subdirectories"
msgstr "Rekursiivselt alamkataloogides"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3278
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-r</option>/<option>--recursive</option>"
msgstr "Rekursiivne: <option>-r</option>/<option>--recursive</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3279
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recurse into subdirectories."
msgstr "Rekursiivne liikumine alamkataloogidesse."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3285
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use relative path names"
msgstr "Suhtelised asukohanimed"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-R</option>/<option>--relative</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>-R</option>/<option>--relative</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use relative path names. This means that the full path names specified on "
"the command line are sent to the server rather than just the last parts of "
"the file names."
msgstr ""
"Suhteliste asukohtade kasutamine See tähendab, et serverisse saadetakse "
"käsureal määratud täielikud asukohad, mitte ainult failinimede viimased osad."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3295
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do not send implied directories"
msgstr "Eeldatud katalooge ei saadeta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3298
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--no-implied-dirs</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>--no-implied-dirs</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3299
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option affects the default behavior of the <option>--relative</option> "
"option. When it is specified, the attributes of the implied directories from "
"the source names are not included in the transfer. This means that the "
"corresponding path elements on the destination system are left unchanged if "
"they exist, and any missing implied directories are created with default "
"attributes. This even allows these implied path elements to have big "
"differences, such as being a symlink to a folder on one side of the "
"transfer, and a real folder on the other side."
msgstr ""
"See valik mõjutab valiku <option>--relative</option> käitumist. Kehtestamise "
"korral ei kaasata ülekandesse lähtenimede põhjal eeldatud kataloogide "
"atribuute. See tähendab, et vastavad asukohaelemendid sihtsüsteemis jäävad "
"muutmata, kui nad on olemas, ning kõik puuduvad eeldatavad kataloogid "
"luuakse vaikimisi atribuutidega. See võimaldab eeldatavate asukohaelementide "
"päris suurt erinevust: näiteks võib see ühel pool nimeviit kataloogile, "
"teisel pool aga tegelik kataloog."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3300 index.docbook:3386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For further information you ought to read the <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\">manual page</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Täpsemalt saab selle kohta lugeda <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\">manuaalileheküljelt</ulink>."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3306
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transfer directories without recursing"
msgstr "Kataloogide mitterekursiivne edastamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-d</option>/<option>--dirs</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>-d</option>/<option>--dirs</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tell the sending side to include any directories that are encountered. "
"Unlike <option>--recursive</option>, a folders contents is not copied unless "
"the folder name specified is \".\" or ends with a trailing slash (&eg; \"."
"\", \"dir/.\", \"dir/\", &etc;). Without this option or the <option>--"
"recursive</option> option, <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> will skip all directories it encounters "
"(and output a message to that effect for each one). If you specify both "
"<option>--dirs</option> and <option>--recursive</option>, <option>--"
"recursive</option> takes precedence."
msgstr ""
"Saatvale poolele antakse sellega korraldus kaasata kõik kohatavad "
"kataloogid. Erinevalt valikust <option>--recursive</option> ei kopeerita "
"kataloogide sisu, kui määratud kataloogi nimi pole just \".\" või ei lõpe "
"kaldkriipsuga (nt. \".\", \"dir/.\", \"dir/\" jne.). Ilma selle valikuta või "
"valikuta <option>--recursive</option> jätab <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> vahele kõik kataloogid, mida ta kohtab "
"(ega väljasta ka kõigi nende kohta teadet). Kui määrata nii <option>--dirs</"
"option> kui ka <option>--recursive</option>, rakendatakse esimesena "
"<option>--recursive</option>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3318
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Backup"
msgid "Backups"
msgstr "Varundamine"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3322
#, no-c-format
msgid "Make backups"
msgstr "Varukoopiate loomine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3325
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-b</option>/<option>--backups</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>-b</option>/<option>--backups</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With this option, preexisting destination files are renamed as each file is "
"transferred or deleted. You can control where the backup file goes and what "
"(if any) suffix gets appended using the <option>--backup-dir</option> and "
"<option>--suffix</option> options."
msgstr ""
"Selle valiku kasutamisel muudetakse juba olemasolevate failide nime nende "
"ülekandmisel või kustutamisel. Kasutajal on võimalik määrata, kuhu "
"varukoopia pannakse ja millise sufiksi see saab (kui saab), milleks on "
"mõeldud valikud <option>--backup-dir</option> ja <option>--suffix</option>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3327
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that if you don't specify <option>--backup-dir</option>, (1) the "
"<option>--omit-dir-times</option> option will be implied, and (2) if "
"<option>--delete</option> is also in effect (without <option>--delete-"
"excluded</option>), <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> will add a \"protect\" filter-rule for the "
"backup suffix to the end of all your existing excludes (&eg; <option>-f \"P "
"*~\"</option>). This will prevent previously backed-up files from being "
"deleted. Note that if you are supplying your own filter rules, you may need "
"to manually insert your own exclude/protect rule somewhere higher up in the "
"list so that it has a high enough priority to be effective (&eg;, if your "
"rules specify a trailing inclusion/exclusion of '*', the auto-added rule "
"would never be reached)."
msgstr ""
"Pane tähele, et kui jätta <option>--backup-dir</option> määramata, siis (1) "
"eeldatakse valikut <option>--omit-dir-times</option> ning (2) samuti toimib "
"<option>--delete</option> (ilma valikuta <option>--delete-excluded</option>) "
"ja <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> lisab \"kaitsva"
"\" varukoopia sufiksi filtrireegli kõigi olemasolevate välistatute lõppu "
"(nt. <option>-f \"P *~\"</option>). See väldib varem varundatud failide "
"kustutamist. Pane tähele, et kui annad oma filtrireeglid, võib olla vajalik "
"lisada enda välistamis/kaitsereegel loendis kuhugi kõrgemale tasandile, et "
"sel oleks suurem prioriteet (nt. kui sinu reeglid määravad lõpus oleva '*' "
"kaasamise või välistamise, ei jõutagi kunagi automaatselt lisatud reeglini)."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3333
#, no-c-format
msgid "Backup suffix"
msgstr "Varukoopiate sufiks"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3336
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--suffix=SUFFIX</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>--suffix=SUFIKS</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3337
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option allows you to override the default backup suffix used with the "
"<option>--backup</option> option. The default suffix is a <emphasis>~</"
"emphasis> if no <option>--backup-dir</option> was specified, otherwise it is "
"an empty string."
msgstr ""
"See võimaldab tühistada vaikimisi varukoopia sufiksi, mis antakse valiku "
"<option>--backup</option> kasutamisel. Vaikimisi sufiks on <emphasis>~</"
"emphasis>, kui <option>--backup-dir</option> on määramata, vastasel juhul on "
"see lihtsalt tühi string."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3338 index.docbook:3349
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option is only available if you ticked the <guilabel>Make backups</"
"guilabel> option above."
msgstr ""
"Seda valikut saab kasutada ainult juhul, kui ülal märkida valik "
"<guilabel>Varukoopiate loomine</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3339
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: not selected; SUFFIX: ~"
msgstr "Vaikimisi: märkimata; SUFIKS: ~"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3344
#, no-c-format
msgid "Backup directory"
msgstr "Varukoopiate kataloog"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3347
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--backup-dir=DIR</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>--backup-dir=KATALOOG</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3348
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In combination with the <option>--backup</option> option, this tells "
#| "rsync to store all backups in the specified folder. This is very useful "
#| "for incremental backups. You can additionally specify a backup suffix "
#| "using the <option>--suffix</option> option (otherwise the files backed up "
#| "in the specified folder will keep their original filenames)."
msgid ""
"In combination with the <option>--backup</option> option, this tells <ulink "
"url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to store all "
"backups in the specified folder. This is very useful for incremental "
"backups. You can additionally specify a backup suffix using the <option>--"
"suffix</option> option (otherwise the files backed up in the specified "
"folder will keep their original filenames)."
msgstr ""
"Koos valikuga <option>--backup</option> sunnib see rsynci salvestama kõik "
"varukoopiad määratud kataloogi. See on äärmiselt kasulik "
"inkrementvarundamise korral. Lisaks võib määrata varukoopia sufiksi valikuga "
"<option>--suffix</option> (vastasel juhul säilitavad määratud kataloogi "
"salvestatavad varukoopiafailid oma algsed failinimed)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3350
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: not selected; DIR: <envar>$HOME</envar>"
msgstr "Vaikimisi: märkimata; KATALOOG: <envar>$HOME</envar>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3363
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "File Deletion"
msgid "File Handling"
msgstr "Failide kustutamine"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3366 index.docbook:3864
#, no-c-format
msgid "General"
msgstr "Üldine"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3371
#, no-c-format
msgid "Update files"
msgstr "Failide uuendamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3374
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-u</option>/<option>--update</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>-u</option>/<option>--update</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This forces <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to skip any "
"files that exist on the destination and have a modification time that is "
"newer than the one of the source file. (If an existing destination file has "
"a modification time equal to the source file's, it will be updated if the "
"sizes are different.)"
msgstr ""
"See sunnib <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> vahele jätma "
"kõik failid, mis on olemas sihtkohas ja mille muutmisaeg on uuem kui ühel "
"lähtefailil. (Kui olemasoleva sihtfaili muutmisaeg on lähtefailiga sama, "
"uuendatakse seda juhul, kui failisuurus erineb.)"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3381
#, no-c-format
msgid "Update files in place"
msgstr "Failide uuendamine kohapeal"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3384
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--inplace</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>--inplace</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This causes <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> not to create "
"a new copy of the file and then move it into place. Instead <ulink url="
"\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> will overwrite "
"the existing file, meaning that the rsync algorithm cannot accomplish the "
"full amount of network reduction it might be able to otherwise. One "
"exception to this is if you combine the option with <option>--backup</"
"option>, since <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> is smart "
"enough to use the backup file as the basis file for the transfer."
msgstr ""
"See sunnib <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> mitte looma "
"failist koopiat ja seda seejärel õigesse kohta liigutama. Selle asemel "
"kirjutab <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> üle "
"olemasoleva faili, mis tähendab, et rsynci algoritm ei hakka täiel määral "
"vähendama võrgukoormust, mida ta muidu võiks teha. Üks erand on selle valiku "
"kombineerimine valikuga <option>--backup</option>, sest <ulink url=\"man:/"
"rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> on piisavalt nutikas, et kasutada "
"varundatud faili ülekande baasfailina."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3392
#, no-c-format
msgid "Handle sparse files efficiently"
msgstr "Hajusfailide tõhus käitlemine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3395
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-S</option>/<option>--sparse</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>-S</option>/<option>--sparse</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Try to handle sparse files efficiently so they take up less space on the "
"destination. Conflicts with <option>--inplace</option> because it's not "
"possible to overwrite data in a sparse fashion."
msgstr ""
"Hajusfailide tõhus käitlemine, et nad võtaksid sihtkohas vähem ruumi. See on "
"vastuolus võtmega <option>--inplace</option>, sest andmete ülekirjutamine ei "
"ole sellisel juhul lihtsalt võimalik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3397
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Do not use this option when the destination is a &Solaris; \"tmpfs\" file "
"system. It doesn't seem to handle seeks over null regions correctly and ends "
"up corrupting the files."
msgstr ""
"Seda valikut ei tohiks kasutada, kui sihtkohaks on &Solaris; \"tmpfs\" "
"failisüsteem. See kipub valesti käitlema otsinguid üle nullpiirkondade, mis "
"võib tuua kaasa failide riknemise."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3403
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy files whole (no rsync algorithm)"
msgstr "Failide kopeerimine tervikuna (rsynci algoritmita)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3406
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-W</option>/<option>--whole-file</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>-W</option>/<option>--whole-file</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3407
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With this option the incremental <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> algorithm is not used and the whole file "
"is sent as-is instead. The transfer may be faster if this option is used "
"when the bandwidth between the source and destination machines is higher "
"than the bandwidth to disk (especially when the \"disk\" is actually a "
"networked file system). This is the default when both the source and "
"destination are specified as local paths."
msgstr ""
"Selle valiku puhul ei kasutata <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> inkrementalgoritmi ja selle asemel "
"saadetakse kogu fail. Ülekanne võib sel juhul olla kiirem, kui lähte- ja "
"sihtmasina vaheline ribalaius on suurem kui ribalaius süsteemi ja ketta "
"vahel (eriti kui \"ketas\" on tegelikult võrgufailisüsteem). See on "
"vaikimisi valik, kui nii lähte- kui ka sihtkoht on määratud kohalike "
"asukohtadena."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3413
#, no-c-format
msgid "Only update files that already exist"
msgstr "Ainult juba olemasolevate failide uuendamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Option: <option>--existing</option>/<option>--ignore-non-existing</option>"
msgstr ""
"Valik: <option>--existing</option>/<option>--ignore-non-existing</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3417
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to skip "
"updating files that do not exist yet on the destination. If this option is "
"combined with the <option>--ignore-existing</option> option, no files will "
"be updated (which can be useful if all you want to do is to delete missing "
"files)."
msgstr ""
"See sunnib <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> vahele jätma "
"failide uuendamise, mida ei eksisteeri veel sihtkohas. Kui see ühendada "
"valikuga <option>--ignore-existing</option>, ei uuendata ühtegi faili (mis "
"võib olla abiks, kui soovid kõigest kustutada puuduvaid faile)."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3423
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore files that already exist"
msgstr "Juba olemasolevate failide eiramine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3426
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--ignore-existing</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>--ignore-existing</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3427
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to skip "
"updating files that already exist on the destination. See also <option>--"
"ignore-non-existing</option>."
msgstr ""
"See sunnib <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> vahele jätma "
"failide uuendamise, mis juba eksisteerivad sihtkohas. Vt. ka <option>--"
"ignore-non-existing</option>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3435
#, no-c-format
msgid "Links"
msgstr "Lingid"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3440
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preserve symlinks"
msgstr "Nimeviitade säilitamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3443
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-l</option>/<option>--links</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>-l</option>/<option>--links</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3444
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy symlinks as symlinks."
msgstr "Nimeviitade kopeerimine nimeviitadena."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3450
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transform symlinks"
msgstr "Nimeviitade teisendamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3453
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-L</option>/<option>--copy-links</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>-L</option>/<option>--copy-links</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3454
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When symlinks are encountered, the item that they point to is copied, rather "
"than the symlink."
msgstr ""
"Nimeviitade kohtamisel kopeeritakse element, millele nad viitavad, mitte "
"nimeviit ise."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3460
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Only transform unsafe symlinks"
msgid "Transform unsafe symlinks"
msgstr "Ainult ebaturvaliste nimeviitade teisendamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3463
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--copy-unsafe-links</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>--copy-unsafe-links</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3464
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only transform \"unsafe\" symlinks. This means if a symlink is encountered "
"that is pointing outside the copied tree, the referenced item is transferred "
"rather than the symlink itself."
msgstr ""
"Ainult \"ebaturvaliste\" nimeviitade teisendamine. See tähendab, et kui "
"kohatakse nimeviita, mis viitab väljapoole kopeeritavat failipuudu, kantakse "
"üle viidatav element, mitte nimeviit ise."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3470
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore unsafe symlinks"
msgstr "Ebaturvaliste nimeviitade eiramine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3473
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--safe-links</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>--safe-links</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3474
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to ignore any "
"symbolic links which point outside the copied tree. All absolute symlinks "
"are also ignored. Using this option in conjunction with <option>--relative</"
"option> may give unexpected results."
msgstr ""
"See sunnib <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> eirama kõiki "
"nimeviitu, mis viitavad väljapoole kopeeritavat failipuud. Eiratakse ka "
"kõiki absoluutseid nimeviitu. Selle kasutamisel koos valikuga <option>--"
"relative</option> võib saada päris ootamatuid tulemusi."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3480
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Ignore unsafe symlinks"
msgid "Munge symlinks"
msgstr "Ebaturvaliste nimeviitade eiramine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3483
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Option: <option>--safe-links</option>"
msgid "Option: <option>--munge-links</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>--safe-links</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3484
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Define additional options for use with <ulink url=\"man:/mount.cifs"
#| "\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount.cifs</refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</"
#| "manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>. They have to be provided in a comma-"
#| "separated list and should not include any options that were already "
#| "defined in the configuration dialog because this could lead to unwanted "
#| "side effects. The list is appended AS IS to the command line arguments. "
#| "To find out about the arguments that can be used read the manual page of "
#| "<ulink url=\"man:/mount.cifs\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount.cifs</"
#| "refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>."
msgid ""
"This tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to (1) modify "
"all symlinks on the receiving side in a way that makes them unusable but "
"recoverable, or (2) to unmunge symlinks on the sending side that had been "
"stored in a munged state. This is useful if you do not quite trust the "
"source of the data to not try to slip in a symlink to an unexpected place. "
"For further information on this argument, please see the manual page of "
"<ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Lisavalikute määramine, mida <ulink url=\"man:/mount.cifs"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount.cifs</refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> peab kasutama. Need tuleb anda komadega "
"eraldatud loendina ja need ei tohi sisaldada ühtegi valikut, mis on juba "
"seadistustedialoogis määratud, sest see võib tekitada soovimatuid "
"kõrvalmõjusid. Loend lisatakse käsureale argumentidena täpselt sisestatud "
"kujul. Täpsemalt kõneleb argumentidest, mida on võimalik kasutada, <ulink "
"url=\"man:/mount.cifs\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount.cifs</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> "
"manuaalilehekülg."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3490
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preserve hard links"
msgstr "Püsilinkide säilitamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3493
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-H</option>/<option>--hard-links</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>-H</option>/<option>--hard-links</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3494
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to look for "
"hard-linked files in the transfer and link together the corresponding files "
"on the receiving side. Without this option, hard-linked files in the "
"transfer are treated as though they were separate files."
msgstr ""
"See sunnib <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> otsima "
"ülekandel püsilingiga seotud faile ja linkima vastavad failid vastuvõtval "
"poolel. Ilma selle valikuta koheldakse püsilingiga seotud faile kui eraldi "
"faile. "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3495
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> can only "
"detect hard links if both parts of the link are in the list of files being "
"sent."
msgstr ""
"Pane tähele, et <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> suudab püsilinke tuvastada ainult siis, "
"kui üle kantakse lingi mõlemad pooled."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3501
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Keep directory symlinks"
msgid "Copy directory symlinks"
msgstr "Kataloogide nimeviitade säilitamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3504
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Option: <option>-L</option>/<option>--copy-links</option>"
msgid "Option: <option>-k</option>/<option>--copy-dirlinks</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>-L</option>/<option>--copy-links</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3505
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This option causes the receiving side to treat a symlink to a directory "
#| "as though it were a real directory, but only if it matches a real "
#| "directory from the sender. Without this option, the receiver's symlink "
#| "would be deleted and replaced with a real directory."
msgid ""
"This option causes the sending side to treat a symlink to a directory as "
"though it were a real directory. This is useful if you don’t want symlinks "
"to non-directories to be affected, as they would be using <option>--copy-"
"links</option>."
msgstr ""
"See sunnib vastuvõtvat poolt kohtlema nimeviita kataloogile tegeliku "
"kataloogina, kuid ainult juhul, kui see vastab saatjalt saadud tegelikule "
"kataloogile. Ilma selle valikuta kustutatakse vastuvõtja nimeviit ja "
"asendatakse tegeliku kataloogiga."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3511
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keep directory symlinks"
msgstr "Kataloogide nimeviitade säilitamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3514
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-K</option>/<option>--keep-dirlinks</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>-K</option>/<option>--keep-dirlinks</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3515
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option causes the receiving side to treat a symlink to a directory as "
"though it were a real directory, but only if it matches a real directory "
"from the sender. Without this option, the receiver's symlink would be "
"deleted and replaced with a real directory."
msgstr ""
"See sunnib vastuvõtvat poolt kohtlema nimeviita kataloogile tegeliku "
"kataloogina, kuid ainult juhul, kui see vastab saatjalt saadud tegelikule "
"kataloogile. Ilma selle valikuta kustutatakse vastuvõtja nimeviit ja "
"asendatakse tegeliku kataloogiga."

