#: index.docbook:3779
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--delete-before</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>--delete-before</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3780
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Request that the file deletions on the receiving side be done before the "
"transfer starts. This is the default if <option>--delete</option> or "
"<option>--delete-excluded</option> is specified without one of the <option>--"
"delete-WHEN</option> options."
msgstr ""
"Soovi esitamine kustutada failid vastuvõtval poolel enne ülekande algust. "
"See on vaikimisi käitumine, kui määratud on valik <option>--delete</option> "
"või <option>--delete-excluded</option> ilma mõnega valikutest <option>--"
"delete-TINGIMUS</option>."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3786
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete files after transfer"
msgstr "Failide kustutamine pärast edastamist"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3789
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--delete-after</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>--delete-after</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3790
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Request that the file deletions on the receiving side be done after the "
"transfer has completed."
msgstr ""
"Soovi avaldamine kustutada failid vastuvõtval poolel pärast ülekande "
"sooritamist."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3796
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete files during transfer"
msgstr "Failide kustutamine edastamise ajal"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3799
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--delete-during</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>--delete-during</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3800
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Request that the file deletions on the receiving side be done incrementally "
"as the transfer happens. This is a faster method than choosing the before- "
"or after-transfer algorithm, but it is only supported beginning with <ulink "
"url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> version 2.6.4."
msgstr ""
"Soovi avaldamine kustutada failid vastuvõtval poolel vastavalt ülekande "
"edenemisele. See on kiirem kui failide kustutamine enne või pärast "
"ülekannet, aga see on toetatud alles <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> versioonist 2.6.4."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3806
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Also delete excluded files"
msgid "Delete excluded files"
msgstr "Ka välistatud failide kustutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3809
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--delete-excluded</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>--delete-excluded</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3810
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition to deleting the files on the receiving side that are not on the "
"sending side, this tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to also delete any files on the receiving "
"side that are excluded (see <option>--exclude</option>)."
msgstr ""
"Lisaks nende failide kustutamisele vastuvõtval poolel, mida ei leidu saatval "
"poolel, sunnib see  <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> kustutama vastuvõtval poolel ka kõik "
"failid, mis jäeti ülekandel välja (vt. <option>--exclude</option>)."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3816
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete even if I/O errors occur"
msgstr "Kustutamine isegi I/O tõrgete korral"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3819
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--ignore-errors</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>--ignore-errors</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3820
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tells <option>--delete</option> to go ahead and delete files even when there "
"are I/O errors."
msgstr ""
"Sunnib <option>--delete</option> jätkama ja faile kustutama isegi siis, kui "
"tekib I/O- ehk sisendi-väljundivigu."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3826
#, no-c-format
msgid "Force deletion of non-void directories"
msgstr "Mittetühjade kataloogide kustutamine jõuga"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3829
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--force</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>--force</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3830
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to delete a non-empty folder when it is to "
"be replaced by a non-folder. This is only relevant if deletions are not "
"active (see <option>--delete</option>)."
msgstr ""
"See sunnib <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> kustutama "
"mittetühja kataloogi, kui see asendatakse mittekataloogiga. Seda on mõtet "
"kasutada ainult siis, kui kustutamist ei ole määratud (vt. <option>--delete</"
"option>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3838
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restrictions"
msgstr "Piirangud"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3843
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do not delete more than this many files"
msgstr "Maksimaalne kustutatavate failide arv"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3846
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--max-delete=NUM</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>--max-delete=ARV</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3847
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> not to delete "
"more than NUM files or directories (NUM must be non-zero). This is useful "
"when mirroring very large trees to prevent disasters."
msgstr ""
"See sunnib <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> kustutama "
"mitte rohkem kui ARV faile või katalooge (ARV peab erinema nullist). See on "
"tulus õnnetuste vältimiseks väga suurte puude peegeldamisel."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3861
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filtering"
msgstr "Filtreerimine"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3869
#, no-c-format
msgid "Auto-ignore files in the same way CVS does"
msgstr "Failide automaatne eiramine CVS-i eeskujul"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3872
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-C</option>/<option>--cvs-exclude</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>-C</option>/<option>--cvs-exclude</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3873
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a useful shorthand for excluding a broad range of files that you "
"often don't want to transfer between systems. It uses the same algorithm "
"that CVS uses to determine if a file should be ignored."
msgstr ""
"See on tulus võimalus välistada suur hulk faile, mida sa ei soovi sageli "
"süsteemist süsteemi üle kanda. See kasutab määramiseks, kas faili eirata või "
"mitte, CVS-iga sama algoritmi."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3879
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exclude files matching this pattern"
msgstr "Välistatakse järgmise mustriga sobivad failid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3882
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--exclude=PATTERN</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>--exclude=MUSTER</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3883
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option is a simplified form of the <option>--filter</option> option "
"that defaults to an exclude rule and does not allow the full rule-parsing "
"syntax of normal filter rules."
msgstr ""
"See on valiku <option>--filter</option> lihtsustatud vorm, mis vaikimisi "
"kasutab välistamisreeglit ega võimalda tavaliste filtrireeglite täielikku "
"reeglite parsimise süntaksit."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3884 index.docbook:3904
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: not selected; PATTERN: empty"
msgstr "Vaikimisi: märkimata; MUSTER: puudub"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3889
#, no-c-format
msgid "Read exclude patterns from"
msgstr "Välistamismustrite hankimine failist"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3892
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--exclude-from=FILE</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>--exclude-from=FAIL</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3893
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option is related to the <option>--exclude</option> option, but it "
"specifies a FILE that contains exclude patterns (one per line). Blank lines "
"in the file and lines starting with ';' or '#' are ignored. You have to "
"choose an existing file to make this option work."
msgstr ""
"See on seotud valikuga <option>--exclude</option>, kuid siin määratakse "
"FAIL, mis sisaldab välistamismustrit (üks igal real). Tühje ridu failis ja "
"ridu, mille alguses seisab  ';' või '#', eiratakse. Selle valiku toimimiseks "
"tuleb valida olemasolev fail."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3894
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: not selected; FILE: <filename>$HOME/exclude.txt</filename>"
msgstr "Vaikimisi: märkimata; FAIL: <filename>$HOME/exclude.txt</filename>"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3899
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Exclude files matching this pattern"
msgid "Include files matching this pattern"
msgstr "Välistatakse järgmise mustriga sobivad failid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3902
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--include=PATTERN</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>--include=MUSTER</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3903
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option is a simplified form of the <option>--filter</option> option "
"that defaults to an include rule and does not allow the full rule-parsing "
"syntax of normal filter rules."
msgstr ""
"See on valiku <option>--filter</option> lihtsustatud vorm, mis vaikimisi "
"kasutab kaasamisreeglit ega võimalda tavaliste filtrireeglite täielikku "
"reeglite parsimise süntaksit."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3909
#, no-c-format
msgid "Read include patterns from"
msgstr "Kaasamismustrite hankimine failist"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3912
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--include-from=FILE</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>--include-from=FAIL</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3913
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option is related to the <option>--include</option> option, but it "
"specifies a FILE that contains include patterns (one per line). Blank lines "
"in the file and lines starting with ';' or '#' are ignored. You have to "
"choose an existing file to make this option work."
msgstr ""
"See on seotud valikuga <option>--include</option>, kuid siin määratakse "
"FAIL, mis sisaldab kaasamismustrit (üks igal real). Tühje ridu failis ja "
"ridu, mille alguses seisab  ';' või '#', eiratakse. Selle valiku toimimiseks "
"tuleb valida olemasolev fail."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3914
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: not selected; FILE: <filename>$HOME/include.txt</filename>"
msgstr "Vaikimisi: märkimata; FAIL: <filename>$HOME/include.txt</filename>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3921
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filter Rules"
msgstr "Filtri reeglid"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3926
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use --filter='dir-merge /.rsync-filter' filter rule"
msgstr "Filtrireegli --filter='dir-merge /.rsync-filter' kasutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3929
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-F</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>-F</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3930
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to look for per-folder <filename>.rsync-"
"filter</filename> files that have been sprinkled through the hierarchy and "
"use their rules to filter the files in the transfer."
msgstr ""
"See sunnib <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> otsima igas "
"kataloogis faili <filename>.rsync-filter</filename>, mida leidub kogu "
"failihierarhias, ja kasutama nende reegleid failide filtreerimiseks "
"ülekandel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3931 index.docbook:3942
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See the FILTER RULES section of the <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\">manual page</"
"ulink> for detailed information on how this option works."
msgstr ""
"Täpsemalt kõneleb sellest valikust <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\">manuaalilehekülje</ulink> sektsioon FILTER RULES."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3937
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use --filter='exclude .rsync-filter' filter rule"
msgstr "Filtrireegli --filter='exclude .rsync-filter' kasutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3940
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-FF</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>-FF</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3941
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option filters out the <filename>.rsync-filter</filename> files "
"themselves from the transfer."
msgstr ""
"See valik filtreerib ülekandel välja failid <filename>.rsync-filter</"
"filename>."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3948
#, no-c-format
msgid "Custom filter rules"
msgstr "Kohandatud filtrireeglid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3951
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-f</option>/<option>--filter=RULE</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>-f</option>/<option>--filter=REEGEL</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3952
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can define one or more filter rules here. Each rule has to be prefixed "
"with the <option>--filter=</option> or <option>-f</option> option string, "
"because the contents of the text box will be passed to the <ulink url=\"man:/"
"rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> command AS IS."
msgstr ""
"Siin saab määrata ühe või rohkem filtrireegli. Igal reeglil peab olema "
"prefiks <option>--filter=</option> või <option>-f</option>, sest tekstikasti "
"sisu edastatakse käsule <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> täpselt kirjapandud kujul."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3953
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option allows you to add rules to selectively exclude certain files "
"from the list of files to be transferred. This is most useful in combination "
"with a recursive transfer."
msgstr ""
"See valik võimaldab lisada reegleid, et valikuliselt jätta teatavad failid "
"välja ülekantavate failide loendist. Seda on kõige kasulikum tarvitada "
"rekursiivse ülekande korral."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3954
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may use as many <option>--filter</option> options as you like to build "
"up the list of files to exclude."
msgstr ""
"Valikuid <option>--filter</option> võib olla täpselt nii palju, kui neid "
"vaid vaja läheb."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3955
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See the FILTER RULES section of the <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\">manual page</"
"ulink> for detailed information on this option."
msgstr ""
"Täpsemalt kõneleb sellest valikust <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\">manuaalilehekülje</ulink> sektsioon FILTER RULES."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3956
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Default: not selected; PATTERN: empty"
msgid "Default: not selected; RULES: empty"
msgstr "Vaikimisi: märkimata; MUSTER: puudub"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3971
#, no-c-format
msgid "Checksums"
msgstr "Kontrollsummad"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3976
#, no-c-format
msgid "Force fixed checksum block size"
msgstr "Fikseeritud kontrollsummaploki suurus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3979
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-B</option>/<option>--block-size=SIZE</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>-B</option>/<option>--block-size=SUURUS</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3980
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This forces the block size used in the rsync algorithm to a fixed value. It "
"is normally selected based on the size of each file being updated. See the "
"<ulink url=\"http://rsync.samba.org/tech_report/\">technical report</ulink> "
"for details."
msgstr ""
"See sunnib rsynci algoritmi kasutatavale plokisuurusele peale kindla "
"väärtuse. Tavaliselt valitakse see iga uuendatava faili suuruse põhjal. "
"Täpsemalt kõneleb sellest <ulink url=\"http://rsync.samba.org/tech_report/"
"\">tehniline aruanne</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3981
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: not selected; SIZE: 0"
msgstr "Vaikimisi: märkimata; SUURUS: 0"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3986
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set block/file checksum seed"
msgstr "Ploki/faili kontrollsumma seeme"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3989
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--checksum-seed=NUM</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>--checksum-seed=ARV</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3990
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the MD4 checksum seed to the integer NUM. This 4 byte checksum seed is "
"included in each block and file MD4 checksum calculation. By default the "
"checksum seed is generated by the server and defaults to the current time(). "
"This option is used to set a specific checksum seed, which is useful for "
"applications that want repeatable block and file checksums, or in the case "
"where the user wants a more random checksum seed. Note that setting NUM to 0 "
"causes rsync to use the default of time() for checksum seed."
msgstr ""
"MD4 kontrollsumma seemneks määratakse täisarv ARV. Neljabaidine "
"kontrollsumma seeme lisatakse iga ploki ja faili MD4 kontrollsumma "
"arvutamisel. Vaikimisi genereerib kontrollsumma seemne server ja vaikimisi "
"on selleks kehtiv kellaaeg. Selle valikuga saab määrata konkreetse "
"kontrollsumma seemne, mis võib olla kasulik rakenduste korral, mis soovivad "
"korduvat ploki ja faili kontrollsummat, või juhul, kui kasutaja soovib "
"märksa juhuslikumat kontrollsumma seemet. Pane tähele, et kui määrata ARVuks "
"0, kasutab rsync kontrollsumma seemneks vaikimisi valikut ehk kehtivat "
"kellaaega."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3996
#, no-c-format
msgid "Skip files based on checksum"
msgstr "Failide vahelejätmine kontrollsumma põhjal"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3999
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-c</option>/<option>--checksum</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>-c</option>/<option>--checksum</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4000
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This forces the sender to checksum every regular file using a 128-bit MD4 "
"checksum. It does this during the initial file system scan as it builds the "
"list of all available files. The receiver then checksums its version of each "
"file (if it exists and it has the same size as its sender-side counterpart) "
"in order to decide which files need to be updated: files with either a "
"changed size or a changed checksum are selected for transfer. Since this "
"whole-file checksumming of all files on both sides of the connection occurs "
"in addition to the automatic checksum verifications that occur during a "
"file's transfer, this option can be quite slow."
msgstr ""
"See sunnib saatvat poolt lisama kontrollsummat kõigile tavalistele failidele "
"ja kasutama selleks 128-bitist MD4 kontrollsummat. Seda tehakse algse "
"failisüsteemi uurimise ajal, kui luuakse kõigi saadaolevate failide loend. "
"Saaja kontrollib seejärel kõigi failide kontrollsummat (kui fail on olemas "
"ja see on sama suurusega nagu saatja fail), et otsustada, millised failid "
"vajavad uuendamist. Uuendatakse faile, milles on kas teine suurus või teine "
"kontrollsumma. Et kõigi failide täielik kontrollsummaga varustamine ja selle "
"kontrollimine ühenduse mõlemal poolel käib lisaks automaatsele failide "
"ülekande ajal toimuvale kontrollsummade kontrollimisele, võib see valik "
"kõike tunduvalt aeglustada."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:4012
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do not cross file system boundaries"
msgstr "Failisüsteemi piire ei ületata"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4015
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-x</option>/<option>--one-file-system</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>-x</option>/<option>--one-file-system</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4016
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to avoid "
"crossing a file system boundary when recursing. This does not limit the "
"user's ability to specify items to copy from multiple file systems, just "
"<ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>'s recursion "
"through the hierarchy of each folder that the user specified, and also the "
"analogous recursion on the receiving side during deletion. Also keep in mind "
"that <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> treats a \"bind"
"\" mount to the same device as being on the same file system."
msgstr ""
"See sunnib <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> vältima "
"rekursiivsuse korral failisüsteemi piiride ületamist. See ei piira kasutaja "
"võimalust määrata kopeerimiseks elemente paljudest failisüsteemidest, vaid "
"ainult <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> rekursiivsust "
"kõigi kasutaja määratud kataloogide hierarhias, samuti analoogset "
"rekursiivsust vastuvõtval poolel kustutamise ajal. Pea meeles ka seda, et "
"<ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> kohtleb "
"\"seotud\" (bind) ühendatud ressursse samal seadmel sama failisüsteemi osana."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:4022
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delay updates until the end of transfer"
msgstr "Uuendamine alles edastamise lõpul"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4025
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--delay-updates</option>"
msgstr "Valik: <option>--delay-updates</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4026
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option puts the temporary file from each updated file into a holding "
"folder until the end of the transfer, at which time all the files are "
"renamed into place in rapid succession."
msgstr ""
"See asetab iga uuendatava faili kohta ajutise faili kataloogi kuni "
"edastamise lõpuni, mil muudetakse kõigi failide nime ja kopeeritakse need "
"õigesse kohta kiiresti üksteise järel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4027
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is strongly recommended that you read the <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\">manual page</ulink> before using this option."
msgstr ""
"Enne selle valiku kasutamist on tungivalt soovitatav lugeda <ulink url="
"\"man:/rsync\">manuaalilehekülge</ulink>."

